id: REQ-pixel-coordinate-output
kind: requirement
name: VLM outputs pixel coordinates; executor owns GPS conversion
status: draft
description: The VLM shall emit integer pixel coordinates (x, y) on a 512x512 map image rather than GPS coordinates. The executor shall perform the pixel-to-GPS conversion. No component upstream of the executor shall perform or require GPS arithmetic.
derives_from: NEED-visual-grounding
verification_status: passing
satisfied_by: CMP-executor
verified_by: VER-pixel-coordinate-output
